Director's Pick from Season 7. Dia Zerva was on a mission to destroy everyone in her path to becoming the season 7 champion. This is one of the most brutally one side matches in US history and reminds of of what made Dia a champion for season 7. 

Welcome to the the last quarter-final match-up of the 2010 Summer Vengeance Tournament! The top 16 wrestlers battle it out in single elimination! The original release date for this match is 08/20/2010

WENONA 
The Gymnast 
HT: 5'8
WT: 120lbs
Season record (3-0) 
Ranked 6th

DIA ZERVA 
Iron Maiden 
HT: 5'9
WT: 155lbs
Season record (3-0) 
Ranked 3rd

Wenona was undefeated in the regular season with a massive 804 power rating. That means her average win in all matches was by 804pts. That's huge. This girl has the body of an Olympian athlete, and she's tough, determined and ready to make this her year. 

Dia Zerva is one of the best wrestlers on the roster - undefeated this season. Dia has the highest power rating this year, having beaten her opponents by an average of 1230pts per match! We believe that is the highest power rating ever going into the tournament. 

Dia Zerva is a monster; she totally destroys this wrestler whom some consider an "elite". Wenona is helpless against this former Marine. Dia gets Wenona trapped in a couple of inescapable holds and finger fucks her for minutes at a time. Wenona comes close to being made to cum, but at least she is able to hang on to that dignity. But she loses everything else - all in just one match..

This is single elimination wrestling at its best. The loser gets fucked and goes home. If you lose, your season is over! This is what Ultimate Surrender is all about! Non-scripted, brutal, real wrestling!
